name: Lights in the forest #1
description:
My project name’s “Lights in the forest” the story about this project is they are forest’s creatures living and hiding in deep forest , they are shining and giving life to the forest. I was inspired by fairytale stories and Alphonse Mucha’s works.


And this piece is called “The Faun” she is the goddess who taking care of the creatures in the forest.
